{"title":"我们“信得过”","authors":["石英"],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":11,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们“信得过”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最近，第一机械工业部授予全国机械工业中五个先进班组以“质量信得过”的光荣称号……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好花红似火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好雨心上落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最好的班组呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要数“信得过”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信过信不过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看手上活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要看手上活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先看他操作："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专跟自己“过不去”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个疵点逃不脱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再问检验员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可信得过？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁面无私检验员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗滚珠掌中托。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干的就是“挑刺儿”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今越挑心越乐："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这还能信不过——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"简直是雷锋干的活！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用户遍全国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能信得过？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面八方信飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信未拆开手先热："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大戈壁感谢送来“及时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峨眉山表扬无名操作者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青云作墨雨作笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都道是：信得过、信得过！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把“秘密”告诉我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好为它写赞歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“秘密”在这儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情深透心窝："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱社会主义爱得真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好产品出于高风格。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席培育红花千万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天南海北到处都有“信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得过”！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}